cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MED, cs.AI, cs.HC

The paper describes a computer vision pipeline for automated interpretation of echocardiogram images, which involves image segmentation, quantification of cardiac structure and function, and disease detection. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG), with applications in medical imaging (cs.MED) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) for healthcare (cs.HC).
